Part 1: Dictionary Task
👉 Task
Create a dictionary to store student details and perform the following operations:
student = {
    "name": "John",
    "age": 20,
    "course": "Python"
}
🔹 Activities
Use get() to display the value of "name".
Display all keys using keys().
Display all values using values().
Display all key-value pairs using items().
Add a new key "marks": 85 using update().
Remove "course" using pop().
Remove the last inserted item using popitem().
Create a copy of the dictionary using copy().
Clear all items using clear().

PART:2 SET TASK
👉 Task
Create two sets:
A = {1, 2, 3, 4}
B = {3, 4, 5, 6}
🔹 Activities
Add an element 7 to set A.
Remove element 2 using remove().
Remove element 10 using discard() (observe what happens).
Find the union of A and B.
Find the intersection of A and B.
Find the difference (A - B).
Update A using difference_update(B).
Check whether A is a subset of B.
Check whether A is a superset of B.
Check if A and B are disjoint.
Remove a random element using pop().
Create a copy of set A.
Clear all elements from set B.


